{"tid":2252944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《波叔出城2》成功偷怕朱利亞尼喺「女記者」面前撫摸下體","createTime":"2020-10-21T23:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:19:48.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c644b73326fd31a263e46eabd6c3b6d7680967","tid":2252944,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"朱利安尼剛剛在被爆料在一個偷拍的畫面裡面<br />\n<br />\n對新電影Borat裡面其中一個女演員 在她面前撫摸自己的生殖器<br />\n<br />\n飾演Borat的 Sacha Baron Cohen衝進房間說 她已經15歲 對你來說太老了<br />\n<br />\n朱利安尼當時報警但警方到場後沒發現犯罪事實<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/21/rudy-giuliani-faces-questions-after-compromising-scene-in-new-borat-film\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2020%2Foct%2F21%2Frudy-giuliani-faces-questions-after-compromising-scene-in-new-borat-film&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c6796dbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/21/rudy-giuliani-faces-questions-after-compromising-scene-in-new-borat-film</a>"},{"pid":"e50ca9500a05a28ae4dcf4b434289d4045c6b47e","tid":2252944,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZJ14g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZJ14g8.jpg&h=b3f98dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bcff8JS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcff8JS.jpg&h=d26f1bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEjD6vA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEjD6vA.jpg&h=0c61a785&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1733962936eaa0713aa0f84b05be3da6b851295f","tid":2252944,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:24:02.000Z","msg":"In the film, released on Friday, the former New York mayor and current personal attorney to Do